  "description": {
    "en": "Bring Formula 1 live data into your home: track status, race control, driver timing, pit stops and weather — all as Homey automations.",
    "nl": "Haal Formule 1 live-data in huis: trackstatus, race control, coureurstijden, pitstops en weer — allemaal als Homey-automatiseringen.",
